@startuml
title Sequence: Edit Company Profile
actor "Employer" as EMP
participant "frontend" as UI
participant "Company Controller" as API
database "Database" as DB

EMP -> UI: Navigate to Company Profile
activate UI
EMP -> UI: Click Edit Profile
EMP -> UI: Update Name, Logo, Description

alt Save Changes
    EMP -> UI: Click Save
    UI -> API: Update Company Details
    activate API
    API -> DB: Update Record
    activate DB
    DB --> API: Success
    deactivate DB
    API --> UI: Profile Updated
    deactivate API
else Discard Changes
    EMP -> UI: Click Back Button
    UI -> UI: Navigate back to Profile Screen
end

deactivate UI
@enduml
